Smoke and Mirrors (stylized as Smoke + Mirrors) is the upcoming second studio album by American rock band Imagine Dragons. Self-produced by members of the band along with English hip-hop producer Alexander Grant, known by his moniker Alex Da Kid, the album is set to be released by Interscope Records and Grant's KIDinaKORNER label on February 17, 2015 in the United States
